---
layout: base.njk
title: "Temperature Converter"
---

<main class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">

<!-- Abstract Background Glows -->
<div class="absolute top-[-10%] right-[-5%] w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] -z-10"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-[5%] left-[10%] w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-secondary/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] -z-10"></div>
<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
<!-- Hero Title Section -->
<div class="mb-12">
<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter text-on-background mb-4">Temperature<br/><span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text prism-gradient">Converter</span></h1>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed">Experience surgical precision with our prismatic thermal engine. Convert between Kelvin, Celsius, and Fahrenheit with instant feedback.</p>
</div>
<!-- Bento Grid Layout -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-start">
<!-- Main Input Card -->
<div class="lg:col-span-7 glass-card p-8 rounded-3xl relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
<span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-primary uppercase">Source Input</span>
<div class="flex gap-2 bg-surface-container-highest p-1 rounded-full">
<button class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold bg-primary text-on-primary">CELSIUS</button>
<button class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold text-on-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface">FAHRENHEIT</button>
<button class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold text-on-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface">KELVIN</button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative mb-10">
<input class="w-full bg-surface-container-highest/50 border-none rounded-2xl py-12 px-8 text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black tracking-tighter text-on-background focus:ring-0 focus:border-none focus:outline-none placeholder-on-surface-variant/20 shadow-inner" type="number" value="22"/>
<div class="absolute right-8 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 flex flex-col items-center">
<span class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-light text-primary">°C</span>
</div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-8 right-8 h-[2px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-primary to-transparent opacity-60"></div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-lowest/40 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/10">
<label class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant uppercase mb-2 block">Standard</label>
<div class="text-2xl font-bold">Room Temp</div>
</div>
<div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-lowest/40 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/10">
<label class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant uppercase mb-2 block">Atmosphere</label>
<div class="text-2xl font-bold">Sea Level</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Result Cards (Asymmetric Stack) -->
<div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-6">
<!-- Fahrenheit Card -->
<div class="prism-gradient p-[1px] rounded-3xl">
<div class="bg-surface-container-low/90 backdrop-blur-xl p-8 rounded-[23px] flex flex-col justify-between h-full">
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
<div>
<h3 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-secondary uppercase mb-1">Fahrenheit</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">Standard US Scale</p>
</div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">mode_heat</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
<span class="text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter text-on-background">71.6</span>
<span class="text-2xl font-medium text-secondary">°F</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Kelvin Card -->
<div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-3xl border-l-4 border-tertiary">
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
<div>
<h3 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-tertiary uppercase mb-1">Kelvin</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">Absolute Zero Origin</p>
</div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary">science</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
<span class="text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter text-on-background">295.15</span>
<span class="text-2xl font-medium text-tertiary">K</span>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Dynamic Visualizer Card -->
<div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden relative min-h-[160px]">
<div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 opacity-30">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="vibrant abstract heat map with deep blues and glowing oranges flowing together in a liquid motion" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDGauLCqfLMwwmZeA612UYtQ_sLaGiSOqkISHz3X_JJiBivsrQ5sfguVriKgRbcjmloOlPGWChGaoVZCa9Z8z8LIQ95KN80xdb0h-KLlQhW9pxTK4G3yDYptYQbNwA0F4VAOpBzN8IDvhDtl3dGGhH8AWenQXhI1FJD3n0KdTjcW2XlNoR8h6orxcoi-XAjRkdo4L6FLXJ__SHfNe-4KK7mI0y6qvVjQP3XaX0l7eH_r-OIzr7HB7KWt3tPai6etxhS3EStcWIl7Q4"/>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col justify-end h-full">
<p class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.3em] text-white uppercase mb-2">Thermal Index</p>
<div class="w-full h-2 bg-white/20 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
<div class="h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 via-green-400 to-red-400 w-1/3"></div>
</div>
<div class="flex justify-between mt-2 text-[10px] text-white/60 font-medium">
<span>FREEZING</span>
<span>COMFORT</span>
<span>BOILING</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Conversion Logic / Formula Section -->
<section class="mt-20 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl">calculate</span>
<h4 class="text-lg font-bold">Precise Algorithms</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Our engine uses high-precision floating point math to ensure scientific accuracy across all scales.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-4xl">history_edu</span>
<h4 class="text-lg font-bold">Instant History</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Values are automatically cached locally so you can recall previous calculations without missing a beat.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary text-4xl">sync_alt</span>
<h4 class="text-lg font-bold">Seamless Pivot</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Switch units at any time; our real-time reactive architecture updates all dependent values instantly.</p>
</div>
</section>
</div>

</main>